Game Engine: Enchant.js
Reasoning: Documentation is magnificent. Large community so questions can be answered. Has a lot of tutorials. Makes it easy to enter and exit combat fluidly. Can be played on mobile devices. Open Source

Art Style: Pixel


- input handling
- representation of game levels, if present
- player class
- enemy classes, including a container holding active enemies
- game object classes, including a container to hold them
- collision detection
- classes for drawing player, enemies, other game objects
- classes for handling audio
- menu system classes
